{"tid":2014030,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正視聽] 聽日林奠生日  18區和你SING屌佢老母係絕對值得搞","createTime":"2020-05-12T17:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T13:19:33.000Z","uid":84668,"like":20,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7c6a7eb8f66075adaf8f92a939bbf8e632f276e6","tid":2014030,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:13:45.000Z","msg":"見到下面個維穩POST咁都正皮真係心都淡埋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">其實聽日林鄭月娥生日關你咩事?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2013774\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2013774</a></span><br />\n<br />\n值得搞既原因有3個 :<br />\n<br />\n1. 係極好既國際線文宣, 戰略價值極高<br />\n記唔記得上年手足修頓球場燒奶共占士波衫?<br />\n結果係上晒國際新聞, 提供左大量國際文宣俾香港抗爭運動<br />\n但負出既成本只係一件正被波衫<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191015/QNJL3JJEY3Z5PI4BOGEITCUCVQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191015%2FQNJL3JJEY3Z5PI4BOGEITCUCVQ%2F&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9Nd5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=4a960839\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191015%2FQNJL3JJEY3Z5PI4BOGEITCUCVQ%2F&h=1fc4e988\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20191015/QNJL3JJEY3Z5PI4BOGEITCUCVQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n同樣道理, 如果一個地方領袖既生日, 國民不但唔為佢高興, 仲18區都有大量市民詛咒佢, 影佢黑白相, 可以玩埋抬棺材MEMES, 搏上9GAG 呢D國際知名網站<br />\n<br />\n2. 本少利大 , 成本極低<br />\n聽日出去和你SING, <br />\n成本只係同平日同你SING一樣, 只係莫須有既$2000罸單 (我相信大部份人係唔會交, 咪搵區議員幫手)<br />\n絕對係本少利大, 唔搞就笨<br />\n<br />\n3. 借題發揮, 借特別日子令更多人出<br />\n記唔記得上年動員到最多人既日子係邊日?<br />\n係10月1日支那國慶, <br />\n如果好似上面個維穩POST(其實聽日林鄭月娥生日關你咩事?)咁講<br />\n咁其實聽日支那生日關你咩事?<br />\n<br />\n4. 癱瘓十八區商場晚市, 增加士氣<br />\n唔洗多講啦, 和你SING最大作用<br />\n<br />\n總結, 聽日絕對值得出, 商場一關門就返屋企<br />\n同意請正評+推<br />\n大家聽日見<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGR38r3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGR38r3.jpg&h=52c556e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f7c6ef70e40231dd96955dcaf195f8bffe3fc2f","tid":2014030,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:15:25.000Z","msg":"大家可以睇埋我另外一個POST<br />\n<br />\n[警世] 以後抗爭日子 10:00PM前一定要返屋企<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2011005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2011005</a>"},{"pid":"df771128651ce4b3eea520a406f1c324cf6a34fb","tid":2014030,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:15:54.000Z","msg":"唔同意既可以入黎交流下"},{"pid":"20e2ebd9848e694ef0116dc92c8ebb71af0e8345","tid":2014030,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:17:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d46745d45fb2713160102bc994b543e8c47d6f2","tid":2014030,"uid":33959,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:18:21.000Z","msg":"國慶同林鄭生日有咩可比性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac05a7215c92d55215976c715a7d54ef5e4941f","tid":2014030,"uid":63639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:19:18.000Z","msg":"拉啦"},{"pid":"5a1f0472ed2f12676f6ab133d5f5c6ba185a198c","tid":2014030,"uid":63639,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:19:47.000Z","msg":"思考同邏輯能力差到咁"},{"pid":"88a49acb3084d4c559eab48cb95908a8bd3c79f7","tid":2014030,"uid":140538,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:21:44.000Z","msg":"如果一個地方領袖既生日, 國民不但唔為佢高興, 仲18區都有大量市民詛咒佢, 影佢黑白相, 可以玩埋抬棺材MEMES, 搏上9GAG 呢D國際知名網站<br />\n<br />\n美國日日都咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你住開共產國家？"},{"pid":"ba791ff18733528e7b21151ea0464e50a1db020d","tid":2014030,"uid":84668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a1f0472ed2f12676f6ab133d5f5c6ba185a198c","tid":2014030,"uid":63639,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:19:47.000Z","msg":"思考同邏輯能力差到咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T17:21:55.000Z","msg":"維穩POST樓主你好<br />\n咁